             was indicted for <rs id="t17930410-46-off252" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17930410-46-off252" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930410-46-off252" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, 1000 sheets of paper printed, value 50 s. 350 sheets of royal paper printed, value 50 s. 150 sheets of other paper printed, value 30 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               <persName id="t17930410-46-victim463" type="victimName">
                  James 
                  Wilkinson
               <interp inst="t17930410-46-victim463" type="surname" value="Wilkinson"></interp>
