                  </persName>
            .</p>
               <p>Indicted in a second COUNT for stealing the same goods, laying it to be the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17930410-46-victim465" type="victimName">
                     Andrew 
                     Strahan
                  <interp inst="t17930410-46-victim465" type="surname" value="Strahan"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930410-46-victim465" type="given" value="Andrew"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930410-46-victim465" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             and 
               
                  <persName id="t17930410-46-victim467" type="victimName">
